title: AG files campaign finance complaint against SEIU 925 (State of Washington)
text: ( Source : State of Washington ) OLYMPIA - The Attorney General's Office today announced that it has filed a complaint in Thurston County Superior Court alleging campaign finance violations by Service Employees International Union Local 925
